atmosphere,

couldn't

luggage

>
> Shadow Cat:
> " Don't be an ass Snow Tech, this is serious! Now find a clearing to crash
> in!"
>
> * Snow Tech Doges the hit and smiles back at the teed off female bot,
going

Making

> * The third bot, just a small tyke of nine, watched helplessly as the two

to

> * On Earth, a small lynx and dove played together. Oblivious to the fact

> light began to fall at greater speed, passing them with a sonic boom. The
> two little forest animals, being babies, where more curious than afraid by
> this monstrous noise and flash. So, they walked towards the ship,
following
> thier noses(Or beaks) in animal fashion.
> They find a small ship in ruins, flashes and small explosions still kept
the
> two from getting any closer. Suddenly, a yellow beam flashes outwards,
